                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-1339-18420404 t18420404-1339-punishment-190"></join>Confined One Year</rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">HALL—
<rs id="t18420404-1339-verdict-2" type="verdictDescription">
